	<div class="about">
		<div class="abouttop">What</div>
		
		<div class="teamcontainer">
			We are a start-up company creating a web based application called Fit Together, which will provide a 
			matchmaking service for those looking for a one-time or long-term workout partner, based on personal preferences. 
			Currently, we aim to target university students who want to find someone to workout with; a key demographic that generally 
			strives for a healthy lifestyle but many encounters difficulty due to factors such as lack of motivation and free time that 
			coincides with their friends. Based on this demand, The Fit Together web application fosters an online community of users with 
			fitness interests that empowers each other to stay healthy through exercise.
		</div>
