	<div class="teamcontainer">
	<b>Overview</b><br>
	Upon registering, members will create a personalized profile by entering key information about their fitness level, 
	workout interests as well as their time preferences. The system will run an algorithm to match this user with others 
	who are the most compatible based on certain attributes. The matching process then provides each pair their 
	partner¡¯s information, giving them the choice to connect with each other and potentially work out.
	<br><br> <b>Functions</b> <br>
		<b>Create</b> an account with Fit Together.<br>
		<b>Specify</b> two activities associated with your account.<br>
		<b>Edit</b> your account and activities.<br>
		<b>View</b> matched users who have the same activity specifications.<br>
		<b>Accept</b> or <b>Reject</b> a match with another user.<br>
		<b>View</b> a list of other users who have accepted you as a match.<br>
